  <title>pciutils-&pciutils-version;</title>

  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction</title>

    <para>
      The PCI Utilities package contains a set of programs for listing PCI
      devices, inspecting their status and setting their configuration
      registers.
    </para>

